	ZipDLL
	Plugin providing basic zip file extraction ability for NSIS scripts.
	http://nsis.sourceforge.net/wiki/ZipDLL
	GNU General Public License
	http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html
	ZipDLL uses the ZipArchive library from http://www.artpol-software.com/index_zip.html. 
	Please read the file ZipArchive\license.txt for details.

Third party python software archives are bundled with the  
DMFC application. The following software is required to run specific 
transformers:

rtf2xml
	Converts a Microsoft RTF file to XML
	http://rtf2xml.sourceforge.net/docs/index.html
	General Public License
	http://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html

The following software is required to run specific transformers, 
but the source code is not integrated in any way with the DMFC.  
LAME is included in the Windows installer and automatically installed.
	
	LAME
	mp3 encoding (http://www.mp3dev.org)
	GNU Lesser General Public License 
	http://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl.html. 



